explanations.reason: The paper focuses on the implementation of Enterprise Resource Planning (ERP) and Business Intelligence (BI) software in Romanian companies, and the study's methodology involves quantitative and qualitative analysis using questionnaires and statistical methods like linear regression and t-tests. There is no mention of any machine learning techniques, neural networks, or other advanced AI methods in the title or abstract. The study is centered on management methods and IT assets rather than machine learning or related technologies.
